NNOOTTEESS
       Textural features include:

              Angular Second Moment,

               Contrast,

               Correlation,

               Variance,

               Inverse Difference Moment,

               Sum Average,

               Sum Variance,

               Sum Entropy,

               Entropy,

               Difference Variance,

               Difference Entropy,

               Information Measure of Correlation,

               Another Information Measure of Correlation, and

               Maximal Correlation Coefficient.

